_sText:
This is basicly iceworld but its cell shaded. I thought it would be a cool idea to have iceworld cellshaded so I did it....was an easy job:
-10 Minutes for the "iceworld layout"
-30 minutes for the Cell Shading
-10 minutes for the Lighting 
-1 day for the overview (Had to figure out how to do it xD)

I think its looks very cool with the lightning and cell shading together.
I didnt want to just decompile fy_iceworld and apply cellshading to it. So I created it from scratch.
Theres a Bombzone in the Middle but you fiest have to break the floor (200 health)
Also to improve gameplay I added ladders to the four blocks. Its much fun to play this map. I included the .nav file so you can play with bots :)

Well....anything else.....then...
Have Fun!
